===Pronunciation===
* {{IPA|/ˈsʌfɪks/}}
* {{audio|en-us-suffix.ogg|Audio (US)}}

===Noun===
{{en-noun|suffixes}}

# {{linguistic morphology}} one or more letters or sounds added at the end of a word to modify the word's meaning, such as ''able'', which changes ''sing'' into ''singable'', for example

====Usage notes====
The plural '''suffices''' occasionally appears (including in one educational publication), but it is not a standard Latin plural.

